## Let's make a `gt` table

Create `states` data frame... 



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
# lowest 
state_min <- quintiles |> 
  slice_min(q1) 

# highest
state_max <- quintiles |> 
  slice_max(top5) 

# randomly select five more
five_more <- quintiles |>
   slice_sample(n = 5) 

states <- bind_rows(state_min, state_max, five_more) |>
  arrange(desc(top5))
```
